#: en/lxde-howto.xml:272
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Though this guide will help you get LXDE installed, the documentation does not\n"
"stop here. There are many resources available to you regarding the various\n"
"facets of the Lightweight X11 Desktop Environment. Some such resources are\n"
"listed below:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><ul><li>
#: en/lxde-howto.xml:280
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    On the <uri link=\"http://www.lxde.org\">Official LXDE website</uri> you\n"
"    will find information regarding developmental progress, a community\n"
"    of support, and recommend system specifications for running LXDE\n"
"  "
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><ul><li>
#: en/lxde-howto.xml:285
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    The <uri link=\"http://wiki.lxde.org/en/Main_Page\">LXDE wiki</uri> contains\n"
"    instructions for customising your LXDE installation, including\n"
"    keyboard layouts, autostarting applications, changing the default window\n"
"    manager, and much more\n"
"  "
msgstr ""
